{"tid":1893901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求推 芬蘭手足孤單地輸出革命","createTime":"2020-02-23T14:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T02:39:15.000Z","uid":228962,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"72e64e53cc5cc09c5cd2c0969156f59f38738673","tid":1893901,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">之前6月遊行街頭識左一位黎自芬蘭既朋友🇫🇮<br />\n一開始同佢只係傾下旅行既野 點知傾傾下變左傾反送中<br />\n佢勁有興趣 然後佢就同我分享林鄭係芬蘭既propaganda既行為 eg:登報（有相比我睇 係政府廣告）<br />\n同時佢都有話佢見到攬炒團隊既廣告 芬蘭左右翼議會都推動緊香港人權法案<br />\n之後大家都會互相send reddit twitter討論 佢最近仲整左條片關於反送中運動 想比芬蘭既人更了解我地反送中資訊<br />\n希望大家可以入去Like and share and comment<br />\n佢真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎完左之後<br />\n再相約大家街頭200萬+已逝去既手足大遊行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0tiX2G3KJAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0tiX2G3KJAg&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAypKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5a1d0f56\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0tiX2G3KJAg</a>"},{"pid":"ca2bc23e7c0879cb9cf5026b5f0ce51a515ec125","tid":1893901,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n<br />\n［黃色新聞圈］香港人 肯 撐 良 心 傳 媒 未，肯唔好扼殺佢地未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"23f4c97b8d179d5f6cb0af1df08cdcff21f95370","tid":1893901,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abb00d2e45000d8ab0301